Query for Creating a Database.

  CREATE DATABASE test;  This will create a database named "test"
  USE test;              This query is used to USE the given databases.
  SHOW TABLES;           This will show the tables.
  DROP DATABASE test;    This will drop the Created database.
  
  
SQL Commands or Queries are given below.

## show databases
show databases
## create the test database
create database test;
show databases;
## use the test database
use test;
show tables;

## drop the test database
drop database test;

show databases
